				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12142815#post-4402526</guid>
				<title>Hairless Guy Fieri</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12142815/scp-4497#post-4402526</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2019 03:27:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zoomics</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5721443</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is one of my new favorites.<br /> Really good concept and something about the format makes it really easy to picture in your head even if you have only watched a few episodes of <em>Chopped</em> or similar.</p> <p>An almost-full 9/10 in my book, so good it left more to be desired but something about it leaves little to the imagination afterwards for me at least.</p> <p>Over all, I hope for you to serve me more food in the future.<br /> +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
